import { useCallback, useEffect } from 'react';
import { app } from '@app/app';
import { handleOrder } from '@utils/handle.order';

export const useLabelsScreen = () => {
  const printTotal = useCallback(async () => {
    await app.labels.printTotal();
    const handleClose = () => app.modal.close('EXIT');
    const handleExit = () => {
      app.product.clear();
      handleClose();
    };
    app.modal.open({
      type: 'EXIT',
      setNewBox: () => {
        app.labels.reset();
        handleClose();
      },
      onClose: handleClose,
      onExit: handleExit,
    });
  }, []);

  const { weight, labels } = app;
  const { status: weightStatus } = weight.useStatus(['status']);
  const { status, items, selectedLabel } = labels.useState(['status', 'selectedLabel', 'items']);
  const disabled = selectedLabel === undefined;
  const { product } = app.product.useState(['product']);

  useEffect(() => {
    const { ac } = app.product.getState();
    if (!ac) return;
    handleOrder(weightStatus, ac);
  }, [weightStatus]);

  return {
    product,
    active: status === 'LABELS_ACTIVE',
    printTotal: !items.length ? undefined : printTotal,
    dropLabel: disabled ? undefined : app.labels.dropLabel,
    print: disabled ? undefined : app.labels.print,
  };
};
